籤詩版本二:
Hapana chikonzero chekunetsekana nehurwere huripo nematare edzimhosva.Ivhu repfuma nehupfumi zvese zviripo.
Kungofanana netsoko yasununguka kubva mungetani dzayo yodzokera kubako kunodzungaira
詩意:
Hexagram iyi inomiririra mufananidzo wetsoko inoburitswa kubva mumaketani ayo.
Zvose zvakaoma zvisati zvave nyore gare gare.
解曰: Rasa zvinhu. Uye iva wakasununguka. Huya nenguva yakafanira. Tsvaga nzira yakarurama.
籤詩故事一:
◇Xiangzi anosangana nemuenzi (Han Xiangzi anosangana naLu Dongbin)
MuTang Dynasty, Han Xiangzi aive muzukuru waHan Yu. Haana hunhu uye haana kugona kudzidza, saka hapana chaanogona kunze kwekunwa. Akadanwa naHan Yu kuti adzidze muacademy, asi panzvimbo pokudzidza zvakanaka, akadheerera vaaidzidza navo. Gare gare, Han Yu akaronga kuti adzidze mune imwe imba yemamongi, asi abbot weimba yemamongi akanyunyuta kuti aizvikudza.
Gare gare, Lu Dongbin akauya kuzomujekesera, uye akazova munhu asingafi. Anonzi Emperor Yaohua. Mumwe weVasere Vasingafi. Chiratidzo chayo ibhasiketi remaruva rinobatwa nemaoko.
聖意: Kumba handina kugadzikana ndirikunamatira hupfumi nerombo rakanaka, kutengeserana kwakamira, muchato hausati wapera, Liujia anonamatira vanofamba netsoka kuti vauye kuminda, makonye esirika awanda, Liu mhuka dzepamba dzawanikwa, mhosva yeruzhinji kururamiswa, pfuma yakarasika iri kure, chirwere hachina rombo rakanaka, guva reAnshan rinofadza
古人: Xiangzi anosangana nemuenzi (Han Xiangzi anosangana naLu Dongbin)
